SENATE JOINT RESOLUTION 277
By Campbell
A RESOLUTION to honor and congratulate Breyer Hillegas on his
selection as the 2024–2025 James Lawson High
School Teacher of the Year.
WHEREAS, it is fitting that the members of this General Assembly should pause to
specially recognize those outstanding teachers who have devoted their careers to providing the
highest-quality education for Tennessee's students; and
WHEREAS, Breyer Hillegas is one such estimable educator, who has distinguished
himself as a professional of the greatest dedication, ability, and integrity; and
WHEREAS, Mr. Hillegas has been selected as the 2024–2025 James Lawson High
School Teacher of the Year, a most befitting honor that recognizes the positive influence he has
on so many young lives; and
WHEREAS, Breyer Hillegas is an extremely talented and compassionate educator who
works assiduously to motivate his students to reach their full potential, both as scholars and as
citizens; and
WHEREAS, Mr. Hillegas serves as an inspiration to his colleagues and students alike,
and his friendship and counsel are highly valued by those who are fortunate to know him; and
WHEREAS, Breyer Hillegas truly epitomizes the dedicated teacher who is wholly
committed to the highest ideals of public service and quality education for all, and he should be
specially recognized; now, therefore,
BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE OF THE ONE HUNDRED FOURTEENTH
GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF TENNESSEE, THE HOUSE OF
REPRESENTATIVES CONCURRING, that we hereby honor and congratulate Breyer Hillegas
on being chosen as the 2024–2025 James Lawson High School Teacher of the Year, commend
